{"tid":404272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落新城市地下搭車 廢老暈倒扶手梯斃命","createTime":"2017-09-18T03:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:24:02.000Z","uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39a280746ecbc88cc3044eef40048fba4347ef00","tid":404272,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"【10：54更新】新增動新聞<br />\n沙田新城市廣場發生奪命意外，早上7時18分，一名老婦在商場乘扶手梯，由1樓落沙田正街巴士站。現場消息稱，老婦由梯級滾下，跌在地上。在場其他市民連忙報警，惟傷者送院搶救後不治，警方事後封鎖肇事扶手梯調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，死者姓陳69歲，調查得悉她在扶手梯上暈倒，跌坐梯級，身體沒有其他表面傷痕，送院後不治，事件無可疑，死因有待剖屍確定。肇事扶手梯為3號梯，一組兩條上、下行線，超過10米，梯面狹窄，只容一人站立。"},{"pid":"5b3fd10b6f90552bd0004473e5cf1e3fe4d3f8ad","tid":404272,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223869&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223869%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Mcz9M%2FyZoDcXS3Cg2jQswU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0ee9e118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223869%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=20170936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223869&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"}]}